OL,3,CFormer Chief Minister resigns from top
OL,4,Ccommittee after arrest
OL,6,FGuernsey's Deputy Chief Minister,
OL,7,FGavin St Pier has resigned from the
OL,8,Fisland's top political committee after
OL,9,Fhe was arrested.
OL,11,FThe former Chief Minister was
OL,12,Finterviewed by police yesterday (1
OL,13,FMay) on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,14,Fpublic office.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
