OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777731064
OL,3,CFormer Chief Minister resigns from top
OL,4,Ccommittee after arrest
OL,6,FWhile he denies the allegations, in a
OL,7,Fstatement shared with the media,
OL,8,FDeputy St Pier said: "I have this
OL,9,Fmorning called the President of the
OL,10,FPolicy & Resources Committee (P&R),
OL,11,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez and
OL,12,Fadvised her that I will be writing to
OL,13,Fthe Presiding Officer to resign from
OL,14,Fthe Committee.
OL,16,F"I intend to seek a fresh mandate from
OL,17,Fthe States of Deliberation in the
OL,18,Felection for the vacancy created by my
OL,19,Fresignation.
OL,26,@pD@VOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777731064
OL,3,CFormer Chief Minister resigns from top
OL,4,Ccommittee after arrest
OL,6,F"Given my role, seniority and the
OL,7,Fnature of the allegations, it is
OL,8,Fentirely appropriate that my
OL,9,Fcolleagues in the Assembly are given
OL,10,Fthe opportunity to determine whether
OL,11,Fthey wish me to serve as a member of
OL,12,FP&R.
OL,14,F"I categorically deny all allegations
OL,15,Fwhich have emerged from the complaint
OL,16,Fthat's already in the public domain."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
