OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777731064
OL,3,CFormer Chief Minister resigns from top
OL,4,Ccommittee after arrest
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Guernsey Police
OL,7,Fconfirmed their arrests, saying: "On
OL,8,FFriday 1 May, Guernsey Police arrested
OL,9,Fa 59-year-old man and a 59-year-old
OL,10,Fwoman on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,11,Fpublic office and an offence under the
OL,12,F1948 Reform Law.
OL,14,F"These two individuals were first
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of harassment in
OL,16,FDecember 2025. These new arrests
OL,17,Fdirectly relate to the same
OL,18,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@oD@bOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
