OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777731064
OL,3,CFormer Chief Minister resigns from top
OL,4,Ccommittee after arrest
OL,6,F"Enquiries into all matters are
OL,7,Fongoing and Guernsey Police will not
OL,8,Fbe commenting any further at this
OL,9,Fstage."
OL,11,FThe latest arrests follow an
OL,12,Finvestigation that found Gavin St Pier
OL,13,Fbroke the States' Code of Conduct for
OL,14,Ftalking to a Guardian reporter about
OL,15,Ffamilies' safeguarding complaints
OL,16,Frelated to local Dr Sandie Bohin.
OL,18,FBoth Deputy St Pier and his wife were
OL,19,Ffirst arrested in December 2025,
OL,20,Ffollowing a complaint alleging
OL,21,Fharassment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
